Write the clone method in the NurbsSurface class.
Remember to respond with a snippet in the form of the following:
```
class NurbsSurface {
    clone() {
        // your code here
    }
}
```

```javascript
class NurbsSurface {
    clone() {
        const clonedControlPoints = this.controlPoints.map(row => row.map(cp => cp.slice()));
        return new NurbsSurface(clonedControlPoints, this.weights.slice(), this.knotsU.slice(), this.knotsV.slice());
    }
}
```
